<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Marta) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ファラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Farah</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リッド</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reid</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ごめんなさい！！
私の早とちりだったみたいで……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sorry!!
I guess I jumped to a pretty poor conclusion...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もういいよ。
わたしの方こそ
マルタを仲間外れにしてごめんね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine. I'm the one who needs to
apologize for leaving you out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ごめん……。
誘われたとき、マルタ気持ちよさそうに
お昼寝してたから、起こすのも悪いかなって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorry... When you invited me, Marta was napping, 
and she seemed so comfortable that I felt like it
would've been rude to wake her up.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もう！
そうならそうと早く言ってよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez! You should've said that sooner!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>い、言う前にマルタが
突撃しちゃったんじゃない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-You were already on the attack
before I could even say anything!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まったく。
人様に迷惑かけない程度に仲良くしてくれよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For real, though. It's one thing to get along with
folks, but don't go causing trouble for them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん、私反省する……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, I'll do some self-reflecting...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミルの事、もっと信じてあげなくちゃ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I need to have more trust in Emil!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
